open terminal 
go to the pemfile location terminal
ssh -i "se_key.pem" ubuntu@ec2-3-231-228-64.compute-1.amazonaws.com
paste the copied ssh command (terminal activated)
sudo apt update
sudo apt-get install docker.io
sudo apt install nano
sudo apt install nginx -y
sudo systemctl start nginx
sudo systemctl enable nginx

check inbound rules

| Type  | Port | Source    |
| ----- | ---- | --------- |
| HTTPS | 443  | 0.0.0.0/0 |
| HTTP  | 80   | 0.0.0.0/0 |
| SSH   | 22   | 0.0.0.0/0 |

systemctl status nginx
cd /var/www/html/(going to web directory in nginx)
ls
sudo rm index.nginx-debian.html
sudo nano index.html


<!DOCTYPE html>
